name: Galactic Chaos
overview: A scrolling space shooter created by Martijn Schutten, Nikaj Eijk and Elvin Van Lvyk for one or two players, according to the title screen it was published in 1993 by Commodore Force Magazine. In fact, while the dev team had already done Relax and Battle Bars for Commodore Force, oddly CF didn’t end up publishing this neat little shooter done for them in 1993 in the magazine.
